author: Paramount Plus
description:
Many Spocks, one legendary legacy. From a cool, logical officer on Star Trek: Enterprise (Leonard Nimoy) to a younger officer navigating his human emotions on Star Trek: Strange New Worlds (Ethan Peck), relive the most iconic one-liners, the critical decisions, and the moments that cemented his friendship with Captain Kirk across all timelines.

What is your favorite Spock moment from any of these three eras? Share it in the comments below!

Stream Star Trek on Paramount+.
Star Trek: The Original Series, Star Trek: Strange New Worlds, Star Trek: The Animated Series, Star Trek: The Next Generation, Star Trek (2009), Star Trek Into Darkness, Star Trek: The Motion Picture, Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan, Star Trek III: The Search For Spock, Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home, Star Trek VI: The Undiscovered Country
